<div class="bg-white text-gray-900 font-sans">
    <!-- Orb Section -->
    <div class="bg-[#E1F0E7] h-[300px] flex items-end justify-center overflow-hidden">
        <img src="<%= orbImage %>" alt="Orb" class="w-[300px] h-auto object-contain"/>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="px-10 py-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">The power behind this intelligence</h2>

        <!-- Point 1 -->
        <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Large-Scale LLM Deployment</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">
                Custom-trained Large Language Models (LLMs) ingest and interpret complex supplier, PO, and BOM data
                across 60+ global sourcing markets, enabling structured insights at part and category level.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Point 2 -->
        <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Global Data Enrichment Engine</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">
                A proprietary enrichment pipeline processes over 12M+ raw electronic component datapoints and 1+
                trillion historical and real-time price points, normalizing disparate sources into a unified
                dataset—fully attributed and analysis-ready for procurement optimization.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Point 3 -->
        <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Closed-Loop Learning via Procurement Feedback</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">
                Continuous feedback from real-world sourcing actions feeds back into the system, refining pricing
                intelligence, alternate-part recommendations, and regional strategy models—getting smarter with every
                transaction.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Point 4 -->
        <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Purpose–Built AI Tools for Sourcing Teams</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">
                From intelligent BOM resolvers to price benchmarking dashboards and our rule-based Price Negotiator™,
                each tool is designed to empower procurement teams with real-time, contextual decision support,
                transforming raw data into tangible commercial value.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
